{"title":"春耕谣","authors":["梵杨","芳草","田奇"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星夜回乡赶春耕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广州　梵杨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路鞭声马不停，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队长回乡赶春耕；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山风呼呼过耳畔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走出公社翻上岭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党委会上忙讨论："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提早插秧破节令。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傍晚才把大计定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"午夜他就登路程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快马得得山头上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏落寒月踏灭了星；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝霞起，残雪化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小溪冰脆马蹄轻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村寨静静门深锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩童忽闻马铃声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喧呼涌出幼儿园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拦马争说指云层。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山顶云间接天处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密密尽是插秧人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎，星夜回乡骑快马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也没追上社员们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨柳青青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四川永川　芳草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨柳青青江水发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红桃白李开繁花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社人家春耕早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宅前屋后大种瓜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨柳青青细雨晴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光灿烂绿水平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社人家春耕早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻地积肥忙煞人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨柳青青燕初来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄金油菜满田开；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社儿女勤发奋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小春丰收喜满怀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨柳青青景色新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水满池塘花满村；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如画天堂平地起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社万年春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社闹春耕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西安　田奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月下布置闹生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天明上山看深翻；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓住犁拐扬起鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记面前牛撒欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁犁湿土往上翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点点汗珠吊须尖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙跟在一边劝："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“书记你年老站一站。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记一听呵呵笑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小伙说话欠检点；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党员没有年老少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活到百岁也是青年。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队队比早"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人比早，驴比早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛比早，车比早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"计划比早行动早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天清晨鸡早叫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粪送早，地犁早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种籽早种发芽早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样样工作争着搞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又比早来又比好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粪上饱，地犁好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼肥，垅无草；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社千般万般好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纲要指标早夺到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春暖花开的时候　慈旭"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}